sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant User as User / Data Scientist
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Webhook as Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant SRCtrl as ServingRuntime Controller
    participant PredCtrl as Predictor Controller
    participant ModelMesh as ModelMesh Sidecar<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant etcd as etcd<br/>2379/TCP gRPC
    participant Puller as Puller Sidecar<br/>8086/TCP gRPC
    participant Storage as Model Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OAuthProxy as oauth-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant RESTProxy as REST Proxy<br/>8008/TCP HTTP
    participant Runtime as Model Runtime<br/>(Triton/OVMS/MLServer)
    participant Client as Inference Client

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over User,Storage: Flow 1: ServingRuntime Deployment
        User->>K8sAPI: Create ServingRuntime CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate SR spec<br/>HTTPS/9443 TLS
        Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation result
        K8sAPI->>SRCtrl: Watch event (new SR)
        SRCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create runtime Deployment<br/>Auth: SA token
        SRCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create HPA<br/>Auth: SA token
        SRCtrl->>K8sAPI: Copy etcd Secret<br/>Auth: SA token
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over User,Storage: Flow 2: Model Registration (Predictor Creation)
        User->>K8sAPI: Create Predictor CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI->>PredCtrl: Watch event (new Predictor)
        PredCtrl->>ModelMesh: SetVModel gRPC<br/>8033/TCP TLS(opt) mTLS(opt)
        ModelMesh->>etcd: Register model state<br/>2379/TCP gRPC TLS(opt)<br/>Auth: user/pass
        ModelMesh->>Puller: Download model<br/>8086/TCP gRPC (pod-local)
        Puller->>Storage: Fetch artifacts<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Storage credentials
        Storage-->>Puller: Model artifacts
        Puller-->>ModelMesh: Model cached locally
        ModelMesh->>Runtime: Load model<br/>(unix socket / pod-local)
        Runtime-->>ModelMesh: Model loaded
        PredCtrl->>K8sAPI: Update Predictor status<br/>Auth: SA token
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over Client,Runtime: Flow 3: Model Inference Request (RHOAI)
        Client->>OAuthProxy: HTTPS inference request<br/>8443/TCP TLS<br/>Auth: OAuth token
        OAuthProxy->>RESTProxy: Forward request<br/>8008/TCP HTTP (pod-local)
        RESTProxy->>ModelMesh: gRPC inference<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
        ModelMesh->>etcd: Routing lookup<br/>2379/TCP gRPC TLS(opt)<br/>Auth: user/pass
        etcd-->>ModelMesh: Model location
        ModelMesh->>Runtime: Inference call<br/>(unix socket / pod-local)
        Runtime-->>ModelMesh: Prediction result
        ModelMesh-->>RESTProxy: gRPC response
        RESTProxy-->>OAuthProxy: HTTP response
        OAuthProxy-->>Client: HTTPS response
    end

    rect rgb(245, 230, 255)
        Note over Client,Runtime: Flow 3b: Direct gRPC Inference
        Client->>ModelMesh: gRPC inference request<br/>8033/TCP TLS(opt)<br/>Auth: mTLS(opt)
        ModelMesh->>etcd: Routing lookup<br/>2379/TCP gRPC
        etcd-->>ModelMesh: Model location
        ModelMesh->>Runtime: Inference call<br/>(unix socket / pod-local)
        Runtime-->>ModelMesh: Prediction result
        ModelMesh-->>Client: gRPC response
    end
